   - RolesGuard + @Roles(...) decorator, checked server-side on every
     protected route, not just hidden in the frontend
   - RbacService.checkPermission(staffId, resource, action)

5. staff_allowlist entity: email, added_by, added_at, notes. Add a simple
   seed script so I can add my own email to it locally for testing.

6. Add rate limiting (@nestjs/throttler) specifically on the auth endpoints.

